  "description": "morph_morph pinned at 1.0 — the far synthesis pole, raw and unblended. No midpoint ambiguity: this is Oscar fully committed to one character. Filter opened wide with moderate resonance reveals all harmonics. Long release, zero sub — the tone floats on its own brightness. A counterpoint to Cave Breath's silence: Oscar fully awake, fully realized, undiluted.",
